Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候 太阳化作仁慈的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓励着地上的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.02,0:00:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候又化作严厉的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,予以考验
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创世以来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经重复过多次的考验 又将袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地干涸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海洋消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取而代之的是广阔的沙海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依靠稀薄的大气层而幸存下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多数生命体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 频临灭绝的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 即使在看起来纤弱的生命中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有那么一群坚强的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们赌上微弱的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无尽的沙海中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,500)\pos(181,470)\fnSimSun\fs30}第一话 沙鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅大人 请别让我太难做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theseus的沙上驱逐舰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被追的是什么人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿度亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须快点去救人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方多普勒效应 是相当大范围的QTF
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰前方地下约100米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,80 60
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道...难道...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OZMA确认
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左满舵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是OZMA 绝对是OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶可恶 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是逮住它的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆・寇因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这...这样啊 你叫玛雅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你饿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃一顿好的 就有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(710,700)\fnSimSun\fs28\pos(320,475)}奥亚泽港
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意点啊 摔了可要被船长臭骂一顿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这里是我们船上的食堂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然已经挤满人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的师傅 手艺可是奥亚泽一绝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 对不住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 坐这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 午饭两份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 特制套餐2份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆 萨姆 萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一下来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪捡回个这么个大美人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 这说起来话就长了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是诱拐啊 干得好 给你加两个捷蜥蜴的蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人做事就该当机立断
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别挤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开啊 这样叫人怎么进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 我 让 开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 让开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米梅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟船长报告了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这可不行 都受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须接受治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤已经不碍事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来一杯吗 提神良药
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夫你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷 真够劲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 大夫你真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为你是去找沙鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然捡了个女人回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么个不对法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被Theseus的沙上驱逐舰追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后连OZMA...沙鲸都出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥常说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为男人 要帮助弱小者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为男人 怎么能见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是个美人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫玛雅的 好像有什么隐情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让她留下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘟神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...这说得太过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？什么？我没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长 是Theseus
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队那些家伙 似乎打算登陆这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 早就显示在卡片上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队的船吗 为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.63,0:13:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是你们该来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 赶快滚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举枪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙 到底有何目的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 是来追那个女人的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队追到这里来 说明...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆 那个女人是什么来头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我 我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又给我惹麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是兴师动众呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是船长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们收到消息 说我们追捕的人上了你们的船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 有这回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把舷梯放下来 这是军队的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为会弄脏我的船的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独立独行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不阿谀奉承
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着船头前进的方向活下去 是我们的主张
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备射击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把枪放下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 愿意这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有着一群出色的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 说的挺煽情的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米梅 玛雅就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 从这里下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅 快 进船去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长 你的坏毛病又发作了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 天性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的们 起航了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开工了 小的们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楞着干什么 给我射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方2000 在沙贼船周边检测到多普勒效应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
